There is a secret rite of passage when saying Chik’In Kaah… Uplift Greg will happily demonstrate once you’re IN ;-)

immutable_data.name: 1 Random Land Plot for the Uplift – Genesis Pack
immutable_data.about: This digital asset makes you eligible for one or multiple “Land Keys”. Every of these Land Keys unlocks usage and building permissions for one plot of land in The Uplift World to its holder. The position of the final plot on the map will be assigned. You can convert a random key to a key for a certain location on the map or just do nothing and let the system decide.  Visit our website, sign up for our newsletter, or follow our social media and Telegram group to learn how to claim locations. Make also sure to follow us to stay up to date about the release of the final Land Key NFTs!
